sources.title: Comin' Round the Mountain (1951)
sources.description: Al Stewart and Wilbert are magicians doing a stage act when they run into Wilbert's cousin, Dorothy McCoy. They find out that Wilbert's grandfather, Squeeze-box McCoy, had treasure hidden in the hills of Kentucky, which they go to find. Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/abbott-and-costello-meet-the-keystone-kops-1955/ Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/comin-round-the-mountain-1951/
